    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no stone chips, scratches, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the leather remains supple and matte, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic feature functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been meticulously stored and maintained to the highest standards. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in showroom-quality condition.",
