    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This car is in great shape and has been clearly well-loved and maintained, making it a reliable choice for your next adventure. While you might find a few minor signs of careful previous use, it drives beautifully and looks sharp inside and out. It\u2019s a solid, honest vehicle that\u2019s ready for many more miles of enjoyment!",
